OL,3,CCalls for cervical screening public
OL,4,Cinquiry as 'patience is wearing thin'
OL,6,FA campaign group set up following a
OL,7,Fmajor review of cervical screening in
OL,8,Fa Northern Ireland health trust has
OL,9,Fsaid it is time for a statutory public
OL,10,Finquiry to be established.
OL,12,FThe Ladies with Letters group said
OL,13,Fthey are "no further forward" in
OL,14,Frelation to their concerns being
OL,15,Faddressed after attending a meeting of
OL,16,Fthe Stormont Health Committee which
OL,17,Freceived an update on the Cytology
OL,18,FScreening Review.
