OL,3,CCalls for cervical screening public
OL,4,Cinquiry as 'patience is wearing thin'
OL,6,FAround 17,500 women in the Southern
OL,7,FTrust area who were screened between
OL,8,F2008 and 2021 had to have their smear
OL,9,Ftests rechecked after concerns were
OL,10,Ffirst raised in a report commissioned
OL,11,Fby the Royal College of Pathologists.
OL,13,FIt emerged last year that the trust
OL,14,Freview showed that eight women went on
OL,15,Fto develop cancer after their smears
OL,16,Fwere misread and another 11 women
OL,17,Fneeded pre-cancerous treatment.
