OL,6,FAt the time, Health Minister Mike
OL,7,FNesbitt said the review would be the
OL,8,Fsubject of independent expert analysis
OL,9,Fafter which he would decide on the
OL,10,Fnext steps.
OL,12,FAt the committee on Thursday,
OL,13,FProfessor Lourda Geoghegan, deputy
OL,14,Fchief medical officer at the
OL,15,FDepartment of Health, updated MLAs on
OL,16,Fthe next steps.
