OL,6,FShe said: "The minister's aim is he
OL,7,Fwants to understand very clearly what
OL,8,Foccurred in relation to this screening
OL,9,Fprogramme, particularly in relation to
OL,10,Fthe service as it was delivered in the
OL,11,FSouthern Trust.
OL,13,F"He wants to understand why it
OL,14,Fhappened, he wants to understand what
OL,15,Fthe responsibilities are across it, he
OL,16,Fwants to understand that lessons have
OL,17,Fbeen learnt and that such matters will
OL,18,Fnot happen again."
