OL,6,FShe said a number of further reports
OL,7,Fwere coming to a conclusion which
OL,8,Fwould be published at the same time.
OL,10,FShe said this included an expert
OL,11,Fopinion from outside Northern Ireland
OL,12,Fon the previous reports published, a
OL,13,Freport of a peer review visit
OL,14,Fundertaken by NHS England and a number
OL,15,Fof learning reviews involving patients.
OL,17,FMs Geoghegan said the new reports
OL,18,Fwould potentially be published in
OL,19,FAugust or September.
