OL,6,FThe Ladies with Letters group was
OL,7,Festablished by a number of women who
OL,8,Freceived letters from the trust
OL,9,Finforming them their smear tests were
OL,10,Fbeing re-examined. Several members
OL,11,Fwatched the committee proceedings.
OL,13,FTheir lawyer Enda McGarrity said:
OL,14,F"After listening to the questions put
OL,15,Fto the Southern Health and Social Care
OL,16,FTrust and the Public Health Agency by
OL,17,Fthe health committee members, we feel,
OL,18,Fas we're sure the health committee do,
OL,19,Fthat we are no further forward.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
