OL,6,F"Their request is a simple one ` the
OL,7,Fminister should without further delay
OL,8,Festablish a statutory public inquiry
OL,9,Fwith full powers to compel evidence,
OL,10,Fwitnesses and which places those who
OL,11,Fhave suffered most at the heart of its
OL,12,Fwork."
